    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor is so hard to reach and it's like a whole thing to get an appointment... i feel like i'm just getting used to the meds. if i just drink a ton of water and take some extra vitamins, can i just ride this out for a week or two until it settles? i dont wanna go to the er for just some shakes and a stomach ache unless its like, actually serious.",
